    "text": {
        "full_text": "„Knubbelchen“ is a small knitted doll that can snuggle, comfort, and bring joy. It is worked in one seamless piece in the round with very little sewing required. It is quick to knit and suitable as a small gift or for charity projects. Includes instructions for both a boy and girl version, with an optional skirt for the girl. Commercial use or re-publication is prohibited. Materials list and full instructions provided in multiple languages. Skirt amendment and correction provided in separate supplement PDF. :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0} :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}",
        "description": "A seamless knitted soft doll worked in the round, with optional skirt for a girl version. Ideal for small gifts or charity knitting."
